    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my ride! I've absolutely loved driving this car, and it's been super reliable for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks great on the road. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for it to find a new home where it'll be appreciated! Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual. The high-revving valvetrain remains precise, and the double-VANOS system has been meticulously maintained for optimal cam phasing. Underneath, the chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded bushings to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and a suspension tuned for neutral turn-in, this driver-focused machine offers mechanical purity that modern platforms lack. Recent fluid analysis confirms the internal health of the bottom end.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
