    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a fantastic find for a driver who values both reliability and style. It has been consistently well-maintained, featuring a smooth, responsive powertrain and a quiet, comfortable cabin. The interior remains in excellent shape, showing only very light signs of use, while the exterior holds a beautiful gloss with only minor, age-appropriate imperfections. All electronics and safety features are fully functional, and it has recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection. With a complete service history and a fresh oil change, this car is ready for its next owner to drive away with total confidence.",
      "price": 34800.0,
