      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014it still runs like a charm and looks great on the road! It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for plenty more adventures. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
