    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power plant delivers linear torque through individual throttle bodies, peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adjustable damping characteristics. Recent preventative maintenance includes updated rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the structural integrity of the rotating assembly. While showing honest wear consistent with its age, the vehicle retains its factory-spec kinematic precision and visceral induction note.",
